reviewText:
Kinda remnids for flappy bird - extremely hard because it catches you pixel before you are in the forbidden zone. The trading cards add some value, as you can either got cheap 100XP or return 10cents back.
PROS:
Nice puzzles;
Relatively cheap;
Trading cards.

CONS:
Bad music (at least based on my taste);
Clumsy controls, both with mouse and keyboard.

If it's on sale and if you enjoy almost unbeatable levels - it's your game, otherwise it's more like RAGE QUIT

